official_title: Culturally Appropriate Nutrition Communication for Mexican American Women: A Randomized Controlled Trial
inclusion_criteria:
* Self-identify as Latina/x or Hispanic
* Self-identify as a woman
* Self-reported as being of age between 18-29 years
* Undergraduate students enrolled in SONA at UC Merced
Healthy volunteers allowed
Must have minimum age of 18 Years
Must have maximum age of 29 Years
